Wearing the uniform of focus—clothes as a ritual to fortify the inner temple. 

A symbolic act of defiance against the mundane, a visual affirmation of intent. 

Clothes as conduits of confidence, not just for those in suits but in scrubs, on screens, in silence.

A silent pact with oneself: "Today, I am sharp. Today, I am present. Today, I am." 

Enclothed cognition—symbolic power over psyche. A silent hack